                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-1">
                        <h6 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Match with a CTO</h6>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">We'll match you with a CTO whose skills and experience align with your startup's vision</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-1">
                        <h6 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Begin Collaboration</h6>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">Start working with your CTO and driving your tech goals forward.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
